OL,3,C'Evil' domestic abuser who murdered
OL,4,Cpartner 'should have been stopped'
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for at least 22
OL,7,Fyears after murdering his partner at
OL,8,Fher home in Glasgow. Mark Keel had
OL,9,Fprevious abuse convictions, and one of
OL,10,Fhis former partners said justice
OL,11,Fsystem let her down, as ITV News
OL,12,FScotland Correspondent Peter Smith
OL,13,Freports
OL,15,FMaxine Clark was a mother of four. A
OL,16,Fchild was in the house when she was
OL,17,Fbeaten to death by her partner.
OL,19,FMark Keel was a serial domestic abuser
OL,20,Fwho had shown no sign of being
OL,21,Freformed.
