OL,3,C'Evil' domestic abuser who murdered
OL,4,Cpartner 'should have been stopped'
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, he was sentenced to life
OL,7,Fimprisonment for murder.
OL,9,FKeel murdered Maxine Clark at her home
OL,10,Fin the Riddrie area of Glasgow, and
OL,11,Fleft her with more than 50 injuries.
OL,13,FPassing sentence, Lord Mulholland told
OL,14,FKeel his actions were "cowardly" and
OL,15,F"evil", noting Keel had abused three
OL,16,Fprevious partners, and had also abused
OL,17,FMaxine before murdering her.
OL,19,FHe said Keel will be considered for
OL,20,Fparole after 22 years, only if he is
OL,21,Fno longer considered a risk to women.
