OL,3,C'Evil' domestic abuser who murdered
OL,4,Cpartner 'should have been stopped'
OL,6,FKeel had also breached the conditions
OL,7,Fof his community payback order, and
OL,8,Fwhen G4S twice attempted to fit him
OL,9,Fwith a court ordered electronic tag,
OL,10,FKeel simply refused.
OL,12,FThe second time G4S tried to fit Keel
OL,13,Fwith a tag and were sent away, was the
OL,14,Fsame day he murdered Maxine inside the
OL,15,Fhome.
OL,17,FITV News spoke to one of his Keel's
OL,18,Fformer partners, Leigh-Anne Hample.
