OL,3,C'Evil' domestic abuser who murdered
OL,4,Cpartner 'should have been stopped'
OL,6,FShe told us how Mark Keel subjected
OL,7,Fher to years of abuse, controlling
OL,8,Fbehaviour, and threats that if she
OL,9,Fever left him he would kill her.
OL,11,F"The violence started pretty early,"
OL,12,Fshe said, "we lost a child together to
OL,13,Fspina bifida, and he put the kid's
OL,14,Fashes down the toilet pan."
OL,16,F"I was pregnant again and he battered
OL,17,Fme to severity of endangering a kid's
OL,18,Flife. Then he made me write a letter
OL,19,Fto the judge to get him spared from
OL,20,Fjail, which was very threatening.
