OL,4,Cpartner 'should have been stopped'
OL,6,F"Was I let down by the justice system?
OL,7,FWas Maxine let down by the justice
OL,8,Fsystem? I think so.
OL,10,F"I think he should have been stopped
OL,11,Flong ago because social work knew
OL,12,Fabout him, police knew about him, he
OL,13,Fhad a history of domestic violence. So
OL,14,Fwhy was it never stopped?"
OL,16,FLeigh-Anne told us about a warning she
OL,17,Fhad given to police when she reported
OL,18,FKeel's abuse.
