OL,6,F"'Please stop him before this goes too
OL,7,Ffar and results in a loss of life' -
OL,8,Fthose were my words to police that
OL,9,Fday. That was in May last year and on
OL,10,Fthe June this happened to Maxine,
OL,11,Fsadly."
OL,13,FPolice Scotland told us they are
OL,14,F"committed to tackling violence
OL,15,Fagainst women."
OL,17,FG4S say they followed procedure and
OL,18,Freported Keel's refusals to take an
OL,19,Felectronic tag to the court.
